name: Strong Password generator widget
author: Vaibhav Gangrade & Surbhi Mandloi

sections.description:
A Plugin for generating random pasword with numbers only ,characters only ,special characters only and with all of them together.

How to Use

After Installing visit widget section password generator widget will be visibled there just drag and drop and you are ready to use. .

Requirements

It can run on any wordpress version.
sections.faq:
What happend if i will not insert length?

If length is not inserted to it will generate password of length 30.
